v 3
d wgini. Weighted Gini coefficient with Lerman-Yitzhaki source decomposition.
d
d Computes the Gini under sampling weights via the Lerman-Yitzhaki
d covariance formula, decomposes it additively by source (share x own
d Gini x Gini correlation) and by observation, handles negative values
d and negative-mean sources, and assigns mid-ranks at ties so results
d are exactly reproducible.
d
d Author: ChangHwan Kim, University of Kansas
d Distribution-Date: 20260716
d
F wgini.ado
F wgini.sthlp
